'''哈尔苏西语'''（{{lang-ar|الحرسوسية}}，{{lang|la|''Al-Ḥarsūsīyah''}}）或'''哈尔西语'''（哈尔苏西语：{{lang|la|Ḥersīyet}}；[[国际音标|国际音标]]：{{IPA|[ħʌrsiːjət]}}<ref name="Johnstone">{{Cite book|title=Ḥarsūsi Lexicon and English-Ḥarsūsi word-list|last=Johnstone|first=T. M.|publisher=Oxford University Press|year=1977|location=London, England}}</ref>）是一种现代南阿拉伯语言，使用者主要是居住在[[阿曼|阿曼]][[中部省_(阿曼)|中部省]]的{{le|哈拉西斯部落|Harasis}}（{{lang-ar|الحراسيس}}，{{lang|la|''Al-Ḥarāsīs''}}）。哈拉西斯部落的成员称为哈尔苏西人（{{lang-ar|حرسوسي}}，{{lang|la|''Ḥarsūsī''}}）<ref>{{Cite web|title=al-Ḥarāsīs|url=https://referenceworks.brillonline.com/entries/encyclopaedia-of-islam-2/al-harasis-SIM_2715|accessdate=2021-03-28|author=Matthews, C.D.|work=Encyclopaedia of Islam, Second Edition|publisher=Brill|archive-date=2021-12-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211211233206/https://referenceworks.brillonline.com/entries/encyclopaedia-of-islam-2/al-harasis-SIM_2715|dead-url=no}}</ref>或哈尔西人（哈尔苏西语：{{lang|la|Ḥersī}}；[[国际音标|国际音标]]：{{IPA|[ħʌrsiː]}}）<ref name="Johnstone" />。除了哈拉西斯部落，阿曼[[扎希拉省|扎希拉省]]的伊法尔部落（{{lang-ar|العفار}}，{{lang|la|''Al-ʿIfār''}}）亦使用哈尔苏西语。<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Oman's Diverse Society: Southern Oman|url=https://www.jstor.org/stable/4330004|last=Peterson|first=J. E.|date=2004|journal=Middle East Journal|issue=2|volume=58|pages=254–269|issn=0026-3141}}</ref><ref>{{Cite book|title=Oman: al-Ghafiriyah and al-Hinawiyah Tribal Confederations|last=Peterson|first=J. E.|publisher=www.jepeterson.net|year=2003|series=Arabian Peninsula Background Note, No. APBN-001|url=http://www.jepeterson.net/sitebuildercontent/sitebuilderfiles/apbn-001_oman_ghafiriyah-hinawiyah.pdf|quote=‘Afar|access-date=2021-03-28|archive-date=2017-09-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170908014214/http://www.jepeterson.net/sitebuildercontent/sitebuilderfiles/apbn-001_oman_ghafiriyah-hinawiyah.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>哈尔苏西语/哈尔西语的使用范围偏北，因此相比其它现代南阿拉伯语言受[[阿拉伯语|阿拉伯语]]影响更大。<ref name="Johnstone" />

